text = "How to play:
The space ship has 4 levels of speed, that
increase when you press W and decrease when
you press S. And with A and D  you can control
the rotation of the ship.

Your goal is to land on the moon with the 
spaceship intact. You do that by having the 
spaceships rotation to be under 30 degrees and, 
a y velocity under 30 and a x velocity under 20.

Good luck"

